TITLE: FlexibleActionsView Class Definition in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet shows the TypeScript class definition for FlexibleActionsView, which extends YTNode. It includes properties for actions_rows (array of ActionRow objects) and style (string), as well as type definitions for both instance and static contexts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/luanrt/youtube.js/blob/main/docs/api/namespaces/YTNodes/classes/FlexibleActionsView.md#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
class FlexibleActionsView extends YTNode {
  static type = 'FlexibleActionsView';

  actions_rows: ActionRow[];
  style: string;

  constructor(data: RawNode) {
    super();
    this.actions_rows = [];
    for (const action_row of data.actionsRows) {
      this.actions_rows.push(new ActionRow(action_row));
    }
    this.style = data.style;
  }
}
```

