TITLE: Getting Continuation for Comments in CommentThread Class in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Method for retrieving the next batch of replies. It checks if continuation exists, then returns a promise that resolves to a CommentThread containing the next set of replies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/luanrt/youtube.js/blob/main/docs/api/namespaces/YTNodes/classes/CommentThread.md#2025-04-22_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
getContinuation(): Promise<CommentThread> {
  if (!this.has_continuation)
    throw new Error('This thread has no continuation.');

  if (!this.comment_replies_data)
    throw new Error('Cannot retrieve replies for this thread without required data.');

  return this.comment_replies_data.getContinuation();
}
```

